lenders.name: E3 Power
lenders.loan_because: We believe in supporting other growing businesses.
lenders.occupational_info: E3 Power teaches commercial and residential clients simple and innovative ways to save power at home and at work. By building solid relationships with clients, E3 Power helps them learn how to understand and control their energy consumption. The process is built on numerical analysis and building science to ensure accuracy. A visual inspection is conducted and the client's energy use is thoughtfully analyzed. A plan is developed to reduce energy use in the safest and most convenient ways. No-cost and low-cost solutions fit into any budget. E3 Power also estimates the cost of updates and informs customers about utility rebates and government assistance programs that could help.

lenders.name: Halsted
lenders.loan_because: We believe in supporting others businesses to help them grow and succeed.
lenders.occupational_info: For more than a century, Halsted Bag has been in the flexible intermediate bulk container (FIBC) industry. Since 1876, Halsted has offered quality textile bags for use in agricultural and industrial packaging. Halsted has become one of the largest importers of woven polypropylene bulk bags in the US. Halsted provides bulk bags at wholesale prices to packaging and bag companies and does not market these products to end-users. Beyond bulk bags, Halsted takes care of the logistics related to importing items overseas.
